'''Iẓi''' (s tfinaɣ : ⵉⵥⵉ, s Tasrɣint : المرارة, s Tfṛansist : Vésicule biliaire) iga yan usknaf imẓẓin, ixwan sg ugnsu. Ar gis ittmunu yan uḥruray igan awraɣ ([[Aḥruray awraɣ]]) urta iddi s ilawin (nɣ ilawan nɣ iẓṛman) imẓẓayn n ufgan.

illa iẓi g izddar n [[Tasa]], ard ittacka uḥruray awraɣ sg tasa s iẓin, ar gis ittmunu ilma iddu s ilawin imẓẓayn bac ad yaws g ubṭṭu n tafrdeddist<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref>.

